data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Idaho Springs, Colorado! This captivating 3 bedroom, 2 bath residence boasts beautiful architecture and a wealth of upgrades including a tankless water heater. Located in a serene neighborhood with mountain views, this home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. The heart of the home is your large updated kitchen with walk-in pantry, complete with granite countertops and a farmer's sink. Whether you're an aspiring chef or simply enjoy preparing meals, this kitchen will inspire your culinary creativity!  At the end of the day you'll love retreating to the gorgeous primary suite that occupies the entire upper floor. This private sanctuary is complete with an oversized shower and a generous sitting area, allowing you to unwind and relax. The fantastic backyard oasis is an entertainer's dream, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying the fresh air.  The large sheds provide added storage. The front and back of the property offer picturesque views of the surrounding mountains, adding to the home's allure. This home is sure to create lasting memories to enjoy the beauty of life!
